/////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
====================  CODEBLOCKS PROJECT  ======================
\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\

Copy the "wiiuse.lib" into the codeblocks/mingw/lib directory (C:\Program Files (x86)\CodeBlocks\MinGW\lib) and add it to the linker to compile


B : LeftClic (RightClic for the joypad)
A : Rightclic (LeftClic for the joypad)
HOME : MiddleClic

Press (1)+Arrows tu use only the arrows (default)
      (1)+A to use as a joypad
	  (1)+B tu use as a pointer
	  (1)+HOME to use an IR source to move the cursor


	  
